{"tid":1837641,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"關於醫護罷工，我想問3個問題","createTime":"2020-01-23T17:09:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T16:17:09.000Z","uid":208834,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fc1068140d0597cb599e2a0cb30b99d2821344a0","tid":1837641,"uid":208834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T17:09:41.000Z","msg":"1.以現時WARS嘅傳染規模(傳染力強)同不明朗性(未知實際傳播途徑)。<span style=\"color: red;\">醫護人員憑其專業知識，以市民及自身安全為考慮，要求政府封關，做法是否合理？</span><br />\n<br />\n2.政府高官喺出席連日黎嘅記者會未有戴上口罩，不但冇呼籲市民注意公共衛生，而且指市民喺普通社交場合不必戴口罩，<span style=\"color: red;\">政府有冇intention去防疫呢？</span><br />\n<br />\n3.政府現時嘅態度比2003 SARS期間更加視若無睹，冇盡最大努力第一時間堵塞源頭。防疫工作仲差過澳門，<span style=\"color: red;\">咁政府有冇汲取到SARS嘅教訓呢？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果1.要求合理 +2.冇intention去防疫+3.冇汲取2003年嘅教訓<br />\n咁政府憑咩要人賣命？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n結論:政府認為人命比草芥更殘，醫護人員宜權衡性命同天職，即使採取進一步行動，亦可以接受。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bc43ea595ff7a3f31404e7aae954564e28868ea","tid":1837641,"uid":162008,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T17:10:16.000Z","msg":"大家支唔支持醫護大罷工？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837575</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"06373513fbd7ffc9acc7ede9c0de50a5dadab451","tid":1837641,"uid":208834,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T17:11:24.000Z","msg":"如果要求合理，但政府唔做<br />\n咁點解醫護唔可以有討價還價能力？<br />\n堵塞源頭先係最有效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b00b4cc5d2240ce918374ddcbdb424de1dacd0c","tid":1837641,"uid":208834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4bc43ea595ff7a3f31404e7aae954564e28868ea","tid":1837641,"uid":162008,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T17:10:16.000Z","msg":"大家支唔支持醫護大罷工？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837575\" data-auto-li